Pattern                                             Type        Category        Example
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
^I select "([^"]*)" from the menu$                  When        navigation      I select "manage_skills" from the men
u
^I press "s" to view events$                        When        navigation      I press "s" to view events
